{
  "video_id": "aFDKHFsVRnY",
  "title": "Yoga and meditation: Subtle Practices for Change: Rosa Vissers at TEDxMonroeCorrectionalComplex",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 2792.0,
      "end_time": 3822.0,
      "text": "All right everybody,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3822.0,
      "end_time": 7062.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to ask you to join me in a little yoga exercise"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 7062.0,
      "end_time": 9258.0,
      "text": "mostly because I really need it right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9258.0,
      "end_time": 10658.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 10658.0,
      "end_time": 13477.0,
      "text": "But I figure maybe some of you need it too."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 13477.0,
      "end_time": 14927.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really quick, I promise."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 14927.0,
      "end_time": 18035.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not going to make you do anything crazy."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 18035.0,
      "end_time": 23990.0,
      "text": "So, if you&#39;re in a chair or standing, just really feel your feet on the floor."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 23990.0,
      "end_time": 25150.0,
      "text": "Ah, love it!"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25150.0,
      "end_time": 26512.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 26512.0,
      "end_time": 30953.0,
      "text": "Sit a little taller"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 30953.0,
      "end_time": 35213.0,
      "text": "and just notice the chair, or the floor, the back of the chair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35213.0,
      "end_time": 37509.0,
      "text": "and take a deep breath in"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 37509.0,
      "end_time": 39452.0,
      "text": "(Inhaling)"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 39452.0,
      "end_time": 42442.0,
      "text": "and a deep slow breath out"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 42442.0,
      "end_time": 45652.0,
      "text": "(Exhaling)"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 45652.0,
      "end_time": 47072.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 47072.0,
      "end_time": 50955.0,
      "text": "Thank you for going there with me, especially since you don&#39;t know me."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 50955.0,
      "end_time": 53335.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 53335.0,
      "end_time": 56721.0,
      "text": "And I don&#39;t know you."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 56721.0,
      "end_time": 59611.0,
      "text": "But I do actually know you."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 59611.0,
      "end_time": 63391.0,
      "text": "I might not know what your days are like here in prison,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 63391.0,
      "end_time": 65211.0,
      "text": "or the stress you carry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 65211.0,
      "end_time": 69655.0,
      "text": "or how your family feels about you not being home."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 69655.0,
      "end_time": 75728.0,
      "text": "But I know you because you&#39;re human."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75728.0,
      "end_time": 78238.0,
      "text": "You may wonder why the heck I&#39;m talking this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78238.0,
      "end_time": 81863.0,
      "text": "Well, I&#39;m a yoga teacher, in case you didn&#39;t know yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81863.0,
      "end_time": 86423.0,
      "text": "and this sense of connection, of being in this together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86423.0,
      "end_time": 88570.0,
      "text": "is at the heart of my practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88570.0,
      "end_time": 92982.0,
      "text": "So even if I don&#39;t know the specifics and circumstances of your life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92982.0,
      "end_time": 94712.0,
      "text": "I do know you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94712.0,
      "end_time": 100304.0,
      "text": "and I imagine you are experiencing stress every single day."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 100304.0,
      "end_time": 104514.0,
      "text": "Through the years of working with yoga behind bars and my personal practice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104514.0,
      "end_time": 106209.0,
      "text": "I know without a doubt"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 106209.0,
      "end_time": 111406.0,
      "text": "that yoga delivers peace, centredness, and a sense of well being."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 111406.0,
      "end_time": 117717.0,
      "text": "I believe that yoga can reduce stress and cultivate compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 117717.0,
      "end_time": 123664.0,
      "text": "and be the key to healing and successful rehabilitation."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 123664.0,
      "end_time": 125978.0,
      "text": "Imagine a teenager who goes to prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 125978.0,
      "end_time": 129419.0,
      "text": "Well, there he takes yoga classes and finishes his G.E.D."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 129419.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131970.0,
      "text": "and once out, he enrolls in community college,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 131970.0,
      "end_time": 136539.0,
      "text": "has a 3.7 G.P.A. and is president of the Math Club."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 136539.0,
      "end_time": 138690.0,
      "text": "This is one of our former students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 138690.0,
      "end_time": 141275.0,
      "text": "and I want everybody who is behind bars today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141275.0,
      "end_time": 144475.0,
      "text": "to be a success story like him."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 144475.0,
      "end_time": 149219.0,
      "text": "This is why I am dedicated and part of the national movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 149219.0,
      "end_time": 151769.0,
      "text": "to bring yoga to more prisons."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 151769.0,
      "end_time": 154217.0,
      "text": "Another student of mine, let&#39;s call her Susan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 154217.0,
      "end_time": 157597.0,
      "text": "came to class and her mind was going a million miles an hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 157597.0,
      "end_time": 159766.0,
      "text": "and she was tense."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 159766.0,
      "end_time": 161946.0,
      "text": "She wouldn&#39;t stop talking either."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 161946.0,
      "end_time": 163997.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 163997.0,
      "end_time": 168907.0,
      "text": "Yeah. Just after few minutes, something shifted."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 168907.0,
      "end_time": 174553.0,
      "text": "A smile appeared upon Susan&#39;s face, and her body started to relax."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 174553.0,
      "end_time": 176313.0,
      "text": "Every time I go to prison,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 176313.0,
      "end_time": 180728.0,
      "text": "I get to witness these small or not so small transformations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 180728.0,
      "end_time": 185978.0,
      "text": "and I want more of them to happen in more prisons every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 185978.0,
      "end_time": 189260.0,
      "text": "How many of you have at least heard of yoga?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 191570.0,
      "text": "Right on. Yeah!"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 191570.0,
      "end_time": 198026.0,
      "text": "24.4 million people practice yoga in the US today, but what is it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 198026.0,
      "end_time": 203756.0,
      "text": "Yoga teaches breathing techniques, physical poses, and meditation"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 203756.0,
      "end_time": 207716.0,
      "text": "to bring about union, to bring all parts of yourself into one place."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 207716.0,
      "end_time": 212676.0,
      "text": "It asks us to realize something all spiritual traditions agree upon:"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 212676.0,
      "end_time": 220232.0,
      "text": "we are inextricably connected like a billion cells of a single body."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 220232.0,
      "end_time": 225212.0,
      "text": "Once you realize that, not just up here but really in your heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 225212.0,
      "end_time": 229545.0,
      "text": "it changes your outlook on life in a big way."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 229545.0,
      "end_time": 231999.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s more than just a soft stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 231999.0,
      "end_time": 235270.0,
      "text": "Yoga actually changes your brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 235270.0,
      "end_time": 238751.0,
      "text": "Scientists have found that brain rewires itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 238751.0,
      "end_time": 241209.0,
      "text": "through a process called neuroplasticity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 241209.0,
      "end_time": 242456.0,
      "text": "and what this means"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 242456.0,
      "end_time": 246476.0,
      "text": "is that we can all shift our behaviors and perceptions."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 246476.0,
      "end_time": 249446.0,
      "text": "So, you could see yoga as a way to hack your brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 249446.0,
      "end_time": 255558.0,
      "text": "and upgrade it to a less stressed-out, more compassionate version."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 255558.0,
      "end_time": 257257.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s cheap too, actually."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 257257.0,
      "end_time": 258488.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 258488.0,
      "end_time": 264763.0,
      "text": "Yeah. Yoga is scientifically proven to reduce depression and anger."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 264763.0,
      "end_time": 268653.0,
      "text": "Anybody in this room is ever angry?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 268653.0,
      "end_time": 270455.0,
      "text": "OK, thank you. Yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 270455.0,
      "end_time": 273905.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a yoga teacher, and I still get pissed off all the time, so -"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 273905.0,
      "end_time": 276155.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) (Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 276155.0,
      "end_time": 277945.0,
      "text": "But, yoga really helps me"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 277945.0,
      "end_time": 280247.0,
      "text": "to set it down just a little bit quicker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 280247.0,
      "end_time": 283492.0,
      "text": "to just let it go."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 283492.0,
      "end_time": 286212.0,
      "text": "Yoga is also a really effective additional therapy"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 286212.0,
      "end_time": 288012.0,
      "text": "during treatment for addiction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 288012.0,
      "end_time": 291066.0,
      "text": "and we know that the majority of people coming out of prison"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 291066.0,
      "end_time": 294281.0,
      "text": "have a history of substance use."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 294281.0,
      "end_time": 298803.0,
      "text": "So, why not offer yoga as a support for recovery?"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 298803.0,
      "end_time": 304967.0,
      "text": "I think there&#39;s about 150 of us in this room as I counted really quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 304967.0,
      "end_time": 307817.0,
      "text": "If you represented the entire US prison population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 307817.0,
      "end_time": 313961.0,
      "text": "about 60 of you would be back in prison within three years of release."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 313961.0,
      "end_time": 316961.0,
      "text": "Yoga can drastically improve those statistics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 316961.0,
      "end_time": 323499.0,
      "text": "and I want more people to be part of that better statistic."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 323499.0,
      "end_time": 326079.0,
      "text": "Any of you ever have trouble sleeping?"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 326079.0,
      "end_time": 328229.0,
      "text": "All TEDx presenters raise your hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 328229.0,
      "end_time": 329719.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 329719.0,
      "end_time": 332037.0,
      "text": "Thank you. Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 332037.0,
      "end_time": 333998.0,
      "text": "Think about why you&#39;re unable to sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 333998.0,
      "end_time": 339942.0,
      "text": "Was it ever because of stress, anxiety, worry?"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 339942.0,
      "end_time": 343242.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m really proud that every student I&#39;ve talked to reports"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 343242.0,
      "end_time": 347817.0,
      "text": "that they sleep better because of their yoga practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 347817.0,
      "end_time": 350532.0,
      "text": "Now, here&#39;s a challenge for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 350532.0,
      "end_time": 354762.0,
      "text": "Consider your vision of what the prison is for."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 354762.0,
      "end_time": 358483.0,
      "text": "Is it purposed to be a chamber of punishment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 358483.0,
      "end_time": 361743.0,
      "text": "where people only focus on surviving?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 361743.0,
      "end_time": 364703.0,
      "text": "Or is it purposed to be place of training and learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 364703.0,
      "end_time": 368876.0,
      "text": "where people can focus on thriving?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 368876.0,
      "end_time": 373314.0,
      "text": "Yoga&#39;s been used for thousands of years to create healthier, happier people"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 373314.0,
      "end_time": 377732.0,
      "text": "no matter where you live or your circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 377732.0,
      "end_time": 381312.0,
      "text": "So, together we can transform prisons into places"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 381312.0,
      "end_time": 386252.0,
      "text": "where people get tools to cope with the stress and anxiety on the inside"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 386252.0,
      "end_time": 392262.0,
      "text": "and build a bridge towards the better future on the outside."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 392262.0,
      "end_time": 399004.0,
      "text": "This is why I want to teach these powerful mind-body tools behind bars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 399004.0,
      "end_time": 405429.0,
      "text": "because with them, we can break this cycle of suffering."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 405429.0,
      "end_time": 410468.0,
      "text": "Without them, the cycle will continue."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 410468.0,
      "end_time": 414728.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll leave you with the word that we use at the end of every yoga class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 414728.0,
      "end_time": 417520.0,
      "text": "which also illustrates this fundamental truth"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 417520.0,
      "end_time": 424270.0,
      "text": "I really believe in: that we are all one."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 424270.0,
      "end_time": 427202.0,
      "text": "Rosa Vissers: Namaste. (Audience) Namaste."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 427202.0,
      "end_time": 437202.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}